style.cssText: @font-face { font-family: 'Comic Neue'; font-style: normal; font-weight: 400; font-display: fallback; src: url(/_nuxt/example/assets/fonts/comic-neue-v1-latin/comic-neue-v1-latin-regular.woff2) format('woff2'); } @font-face { font-family: 'Comic Neue'; font-style: normal; font-weight: 700; font-display: fallback; src: url(/_nuxt/example/assets/fonts/comic-neue-v1-latin/comic-neue-v1-latin-700.woff2) format('woff2'); } .font-comic-neue { font-family: var(--family, 'Arial','sans-serif'); font-style: var(--font-style, normal); font-weight: var(--font-weight, 400); } .font { --family: var(--font-family); }
